{{ŚćĀŚĻ≤ŚćĀšļĆśĒĮ|qq=}} '''Otsu''' (šĻô, "kinoto") is the second of the {{ill|Heavenly Stems|lt=Ten Heavenly Stems|8=en|ja|ŚćĀŚĻ≤|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Heavenly Stems|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Heavenly Stems|qq=}}.<ref>https://www.bing.com/ck/a?!&&p=4c9a92862e1b9aabc3b009cfd0a01023a23ad178c0d8269211d19906d318e4d6JmltdHM9MTc0MzAzMzYwMA&ptn=3&ver=2&hsh=4&fclid=3e6f989f-7779-62d7-1cd7-8d247648633d&psq=Kinoto+(%e4%b9%99)&u=a1aHR0cHM6Ly9qaXRlbm9uLmNvbS93b3JkLzUwNTI&ntb=1</ref><ref>https://www.bing.com/ck/a?!&&p=1be7966818ee6798e5c1fdd09171ddb9d95fab26ae826d08015e33742959ef07JmltdHM9MTc0MzAzMzYwMA&ptn=3&ver=2&hsh=4&fclid=3e6f989f-7779-62d7-1cd7-8d247648633d&psq=Kinoto+(%e4%b9%99)&u=a1aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cudGFub3NoaWlqYXBhbmVzZS5jb20vZGljdGlvbmFyeS9lbnRyeV9kZXRhaWxzLmNmbT9lbnRyeV9pZD0xNzI0MA&ntb=1</ref><ref>https://www.bing.com/ck/a?!&&p=4f4babef6238b7c7cd9b5847a6f52b83af1f7888cd92e4da51952307ac659dd0JmltdHM9MTc0MzAzMzYwMA&ptn=3&ver=2&hsh=4&fclid=3e6f989f-7779-62d7-1cd7-8d247648633d&psq=Kinoto+(%e4%b9%99)&u=a1aHR0cHM6Ly9qbGVhcm4ubmV0L2RpY3Rpb25hcnkvJUU0JUI5JTk5LSVFMyU4MSU4RCVFMyU4MSVBRSVFMyU4MSVBOA&ntb=1</ref><ref>https://www.bing.com/ck/a?!&&p=8a1a36e31997673c3990a8a25fe11ee979cd2b1283c0c44659ae224f81bb0656JmltdHM9MTc0MzAzMzYwMA&ptn=3&ver=2&hsh=4&fclid=3e6f989f-7779-62d7-1cd7-8d247648633d&psq=Kinoto+(%e4%b9%99)&u=a1aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cud29yZHNlbnNlLmV1L2tpbm90by8&ntb=1</ref>
According to the {{ill|Yin-Yang Five Elements theory|ja|ťôįťôĹšļĒŤ°ĆŤ™¨|1=Yin-Yang and Wuxing Theory|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin-Yang Five Elements theory|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin-Yang and Wuxing Theory|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin-Yang Five Elements theory|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin-Yang and Wuxing Theory|qq=}}, it is assigned to the {{ill|yin|ja|ťôį|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/yin|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/yin|qq=}} aspect of the {{ill|Wood (wuxing)|lt=wood element|ja|Wood (śú®)|1=Wood (wuxing)|lt=Wood (śú®)|2=uk|3=–Ē–Ķ—Ä–Ķ–≤–ĺ (–Ķ–Ľ–Ķ–ľ–Ķ–Ĺ—ā)|4=id|5=Kayu (Wu Xing)|6=ms|7=Kayu (Wu Xing)|8=bcl|9=Kahoy (wuxing)|10=ca|11=Fusta (wuxing)|12=it|13=Legno (elemento)|14=es|15=Madera (Wu Xing)|16=nl|17=Hout (element)|18=vi|19=MŠĽôc (NgŇ© h√†nh)|20=tr|21=Tahta (klasik element)|22=ta|23=ŗģģŗģįŗģģŗĮć (ŗģöŗĮÄŗģ© ŗģģŗĮÜŗģĮŗĮćŗģĮŗģŅŗģĮŗģ≤ŗĮć)|2=it|3=Legno (elemento)|4=es|5=Madera (Wu Xing)|6=tr|7=Tahta (klasik element)|1=Wood (wuxing)|lt=Wood (śú®)|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Wood (wuxing)|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Wood (wuxing)|13=User:Immanuelle/Wood (wuxing)|qq=}}. Hence, in Japan, it is also referred to as "kinoto" (meaning "younger brother of wood").
